{"tid":404163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩兄弟為錢嘈 33歲細佬打到35歲大佬周身傷","createTime":"2017-09-17T23:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T03:29:11.000Z","uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"971e8b370a1c06a49ae7e92f1ea164cc6ff6cdc6","tid":404163,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:12:31.000Z","msg":"2017-09-18 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170918&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57223525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170918%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57223525&d=dfVp40sK0uRlKjoKzgMyZROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=26af3653\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170918%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57223525&h=51095be8\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170918&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57223525</a><br />\n<br />\n凌晨零時許，一名35歲姓香男事主，在大圍顯徑邨寓所，因金錢問題與33歲胞弟爭執，其間被對方懷疑以硬物襲擊及恐嚇。男事主身體多處受傷清醒送院治理。警方初步調查後，以嫌刑事恐嚇及襲擊致造成實際身體傷害拘捕胞弟，案件交沙田警區刑事調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"2ec4b07138ff487f787273e33d8d4c273a42abab","tid":404163,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833b879a88c6811b7610a7b45cc61b6d2d0d725a","tid":404163,"uid":147225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:25:57.000Z","msg":"呢排真係多古怪命案/傷人案"},{"pid":"135f64841073ac07b9d750738292f4550c50b7b6","tid":404163,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:37:16.000Z","msg":"尋日係爭淥麵，今日係爭錢，聽日會爭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76cca4901c8e76852c47f991ca2664ce7ecc30f1","tid":404163,"uid":91196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17